subject: Football (College)
Halls of Fame
lead_paragraph: The starting quarterbacks in the 1996 Fiesta Bowl, Tommie Frazier of Nebraska and Danny Wuerffel of Florida, were chosen for induction into the College Football Hall of Fame.
